schema.description: This class can be used as the Type for any secret entity represented as Value, ValueCertificateThumbprint, EncryptionAlgorithm. In this case, "Value" is a secret and the "valueThumbprint" represents the certificate thumbprint of the value. The algorithm field is mainly for future usage to potentially allow different entities encrypted using different algorithms.
